<h3>Track Consultations From Social Media</h3>
<p>Set up UTM parameters on every link you share from social media. When a potential client clicks a link in your LinkedIn post and books a consultation, Google Analytics attributes that conversion to LinkedIn.</p>
<p>Your intake form should also ask "How did you hear about us?" with social media as an option. Cross-reference these self-reported answers with your UTM data for the most accurate picture.</p>
<p>For firms spending $2,000+ monthly on social media (ads, tools, time), the target return is 3-5 consultations per month from social channels. At an average case value of $5,000-$50,000 depending on practice area, even one client per month makes the investment worthwhile.</p>
